As you can see, here we have a multiline, key string. However, the configuration value must all be on one line. You must make this a single line string with explicit `\n` newline characters.  You can convert this automatically with the following command: `cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa | sed '$!s/$/\\n/' | tr -d '\n'`.

